sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor M as Maintainer
    participant G as Git
    participant D as Drone CI
    participant H as helm CLI in CI
    participant GCS as gs://peaka-chart/
    actor C as Customer

    M->>M: Edit chart/values.yaml<br/>(image tags) and Chart.yaml (version)
    M->>G: git commit -am "Update image versions"
    M->>G: git commit -am "Release chart 1.0.12"
    M->>G: git tag v1.0.12
    M->>G: git push --tags

    G->>D: tag event
    D->>D: validate signed pipeline (HMAC)

    D->>H: version-check<br/>tag minus 'v' == Chart.yaml#version?
    alt mismatch
        D->>M: pipeline FAILS
    end

    D->>H: helm dependency update + build
    H->>H: pull bitnami / minio / traefik / permify subcharts
    D->>H: helm package . → peaka-1.0.12.tgz

    D->>GCS: gsutil cp gs://peaka-chart/charts/index.yaml /tmp/
    D->>H: helm repo index . --merge /tmp/index.yaml<br/>--url https://peaka-chart.storage.googleapis.com/charts

    D->>GCS: gsutil cp index.yaml gs://peaka-chart/charts/
    D->>GCS: gsutil cp peaka-1.0.12.tgz gs://peaka-chart/charts/

    Note over C: later...
    C->>C: helm repo update
    C->>GCS: GET /charts/index.yaml
    C->>GCS: GET /charts/peaka-1.0.12.tgz
    C->>C: helm upgrade mypeaka peaka/peaka<br/>-f my-values.yaml

    Note over M,C: 📂 Files to skim<br/>.drone.yml — pipeline steps<br/>chart/Chart.yaml — version, deps<br/>chart/values.yaml — what the customer overrides<br/>docs/runbooks/chart-release.md — release runbook<br/>docs/extras/gotchas_invariants.md#8 — version-tag invariant
